'''摩尔多瓦总统选举'''于2016年10月30日举行。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-20908466-alegerile-prezidentiale-din-moldova-vor-tine-30-octombrie.htm |title=Alegerile prezidentiale din R. Moldova se vor tine pe 30 octombrie |work=HotNews.ro |author=G. S. |date=1 April 2016 |accessdate=2016-11-09 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104080605/http://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-esential-20908466-alegerile-prezidentiale-din-moldova-vor-tine-30-octombrie.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>这是[[摩尔多瓦|摩尔多瓦]]自1996年以来的第一次总统直接选举。摩尔多瓦1991年独立后，前两位总统均为全民直选产生。1996年总统选举后，议会于2000年修宪决定总统由议会选举产生。2016年3月4日，摩宪法法院决定恢复全民投票选举总统。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.publika.md/curtea-constitutionala-a-decis-presedintele-tarii-va-fi-ales-prin-vot-direct-de-catre-popor-_2551711.html |title=The Constitutional Court of Moldova has decided: the country's president will be directly elected by the people |publisher=publika.md |accessdate=4 March 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108083658/http://www.publika.md/curtea-constitutionala-a-decis-presedintele-tarii-va-fi-ales-prin-vot-direct-de-catre-popor-_2551711.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://unimedia.info/stiri/video-ultima-ora-curtea-constitutionala-presedintele-va-fi-ales-direct-de-popor-110682.html |title=The Constitutional Court: the president will be elected by the people |publisher=Unimedia.info |accessdate=4 March 2016 |archive-date=2016-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507210008/http://unimedia.info/stiri/video-ultima-ora-curtea-constitutionala-presedintele-va-fi-ales-direct-de-popor-110682.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

